<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/welcome-page.css">
    <title>Welcome to the Quiz</title>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1 class="quiz-heading">Welcome to the Quiz</h1>
        <p class="quiz-description">Click the button below to start the quiz</p>
    </header>

    <form action="quiz" class="quiz-form">
        <input type="submit" value="Start Quiz" class="start-quiz-button">
    </form>

    <section class="quiz-details">
        <h2 class="quiz-subheading">Description:</h2>
        <p class="quiz-description">
            Embark on an enthralling journey through the cosmos in "Lost Memories in Space," a gripping interactive quest that unfolds with each decision you make. <br><br>
            The narrative revolves around an individual awakening in a cryo chamber, grappling with amnesia, and navigating a myriad of choices that shape their destiny.
        </p>

        <img src="img/quiz_logo.png" alt="Project Image" class="project-image">

        <div class="project-description">
            <p>Additional information about the project:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Frontend User Interface</li>
                <li>Backend Server Architecture</li>
                <li>Database Integration</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
</body>

</html>
